quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,62,"Ala inna awliyaa Allahila khawfun AAalayhim wala hum yahzanoon"
  10,63,"Allatheena amanoo wakanooyattaqoon"
  10,64,"Lahumu albushra fee alhayatiaddunya wafee al-akhirati latabdeela likalimati Allahi thalika huwaalfawzu alAAatheem"
  10,65,"Wala yahzunka qawluhum innaalAAizzata lillahi jameeAAan huwa assameeAAualAAaleem"
  10,66,"Ala inna lillahi man fee assamawatiwaman fee al-ardi wama yattabiAAu allatheenayadAAoona min dooni Allahi shurakaa inyattabiAAoona illa aththanna wa-inhum illa yakhrusoon"
  10,67,"Huwa allathee jaAAala lakumu allaylalitaskunoo feehi wannahara mubsiran innafee thalika laayatin liqawmin yasmaAAoon"
  10,68,"Qaloo ittakhatha Allahuwaladan subhanahu huwa alghaniyyu lahu ma fee assamawatiwama fee al-ardi in AAindakum min sultaninbihatha ataqooloona AAala Allahi ma lataAAlamoon"
  10,69,"Qul inna allatheena yaftaroona AAalaAllahi alkathiba la yuflihoon"
  10,70,"MataAAun fee addunyathumma ilayna marjiAAuhum thumma nutheequhumu alAAathabaashshadeeda bima kanoo yakfuroon"
